AU LANDON, avait 18 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Mahaut Du Tourneau. Il est décédé le 7 janvier 1182, à Argentan, Orne, Basse-Normandie, France, à l’âge de 61 ans."},"de":{"7 January 1121–7 January 1182":"7. Januar 1121–7. Januar 1182","1121–1182":"1121–1182","1125–Female":"1125–Verstorben","1127–Female":"1127–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1120–Female":"1120–Verstorben","1145–1182":"1145–1182","1101–1182":"1101–1182","1104–Female":"1104–Verstorben","1127":"1127","7 January 1182":"7. Januar 1182","1104":"1104","7 January 1121":"7. Januar 1121","1125":"1125","1145":"1145","1101":"1101","1121":"1121","1120":"1120","7 Jan 1182":"7. Januar 1182","1182":"1182","Argentan, Orne, Basse-Normandie, France":"Argentan, Orne, Basse-Normandie, Frankreich","Chateau-Landon, Gatinais, France":"Château-Landon, Seine-et-Marne, Île-de-France, Frankreich","France":"Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Als Sir Robert Clement am 7. Januar 1121 in Château-Landon, Seine-et-Marne, Île-de-France, Frankreich geboren wurde, war sein Vater Lord Robert I d'Nemours Clement Lord 20 und seine Mutter Beline DE CHATEAU LANDON 18. Er hatte mit Mahaut Du Tourneau mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb am 7. Januar 1182 im Alter von 61 Jahren in Argentan, Orne, Basse-Normandie, Frankreich."},"ht":{"7 January 1121–7 January 1182":"7 January 1121–7 January 1182","1121–1182":"1121–1182","1125–Female":"1125–Desede","1127–Female":"1127–Desede","–Male":"Desede","1120–Female":"1120–Desede","1145–1182":"1145–1182","1101–1182":"1101–1182","1104–Female":"1104–Desede","1127":"1127","7 January 1182":"7 January 1182","1104":"1104","7 January 1121":"7 January 1121","1125":"1125","1145":"1145","1101":"1101","1121":"1121","1120":"1120","7 Jan 1182":"7 January 1182","1182":"1182","Argentan, Orne, Basse-Normandie, France":"Argentan, Orne, Basse-Normandie, France","Chateau-Landon, Gatinais, France":"Château-Landon, Seine-et-Marne, Île-de-France, France","France":"France"},"hu":{"7 January 1121–7 January 1182":"1121. január 7.–1182. jan